00:01:59.080 --> 00:02:00.920
 That's how it looks now. 

00:02:02.300 --> 00:02:05.360
 Halve it in length. 

00:02:13.900 --> 00:02:17.460
 Fold down the upper third of the narrow piece. 

00:02:18.880 --> 00:02:20.880
 This will be the head of your swan. 

00:02:29.420 --> 00:02:31.420
 Hold the lower end of the neck firmly 

00:02:31.760 --> 00:02:34.580
 and pull the body down with the other hand. 

00:02:35.680 --> 00:02:39.920
 You have to push the body against the table so that the swan stops. 

00:02:45.380 --> 00:02:47.380
 Keep your head in shape and shape 

00:02:47.600 --> 00:02:50.320
 You have already folded a swan from a banknote. 

